column12: You know, florzinha, that Black Scrawl has almost completely taken you over.
But goddamn, we had fun, huh? Killing and killing and more killing... What a rush!
Wait... No. No, no, no! It wasn't fun at all!
I turned you into a killing machine! I spread evil and chaos around the world!
But it all feels so empty now! Why!? I don't understand!
Sorry, looks like you stayed inside me for a little too long...florzinha.
Stop! Don't be nice to me! Don't make me feel like this!
